Package org.jivesoftware.openfire.entitycaps

Implementation of Entity Capabilities (XEP-0115).

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EntityCapabilities Contains identities and supported features describing client capabilities for an entity.
EntityCapabilitiesManager Implements server side mechanics for XEP-0115: "Entity Capabilities" Version 1.4 In particular, EntityCapabilitiesManager is useful for processing "filtered-notifications" for use with Pubsub (XEP-0060) for contacts that may not want to receive notifications for all payload types.
